<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.6.4">
<l>kuṉṟālmā ritaṭut tavaṉaikkula vēḻamaṉṟu</l>
<l>poṉṟāmai yataṉuk karuḷcey tapōrēṟṟai</l>
<l>yaṉṟāviṉ naṟuney yamarntuṇṇa vaṇiyaḻuntūr</l>
<l>niṉṟāṉai yaṭiyēṉ kaṇṭukoṇṭuni ṟaintēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having seen for myself the one who blocked the rain with a hill,</l>
<l>The battle bull who once granted a blessing</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the noble elephant would not die,</l>
<l>The one who stands in beautiful Aḻuntūr since fragrant butter from cows</l>
<l>Is kept there, I, his servant, was fulfilled.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
